Topic :: Software Development :: Libraries :: Python Modules
info.description:
PyPo is an onion-skin thick layer on libpq for PostgreSQL. It can be used for
the foundation for other database wrappers, or as a database wrapper itself.

It currently supports about 80% of the functions provided by libpq.
